summary: Stress is actually a good thing. It lets you know that something’s wrong or that maybe you should make a few changes or try...
body: Stress is actually a good thing. It lets you know that something’s wrong or that maybe you should make a few changes or try something new. But, too much stress isn’t so good. That’s why it’s important to find healthy ways to relieve your stress. I like to work out at the gym or practice my spear moves and potential Final Smash, myself. I also know a girl who, uh, sings death metal at a karaoke bar. Whatever works, I guess.
